{
  "texts": [
    "This searching process is time-consuming and costly [1].",
    "On one hand, there could be hundreds of types of information.",
    "The regulator has to manually type keywords related to all these types of information to completely check the financial documents, which is time-consuming.",
    "Besides that, many sentences can match the same keyword [3].",
    "The regulator must select the right sentences describing each type of information to understand whether the sentences correctly explain the corresponding type of information."
  ]
}